    "body": "### Checked for duplicates?\r\n\r\n- [X] This issue is not a duplicate\r\n\r\n### What are the steps to reproduce this bug?\r\n\r\n1. [Settings] -> [Language] -> Select any language other than the system language\r\n   - In the following example, the system language is Spanish, and the language configured on AnkiDroid is German.\r\n2. (Optional) Sync to check if the issue of #13369 is reproduced\r\n   - The issue (13369) wasn't reproduced on my environment, so I suppose that the issue and the following issue are separate ones.\r\n\r\n3. Tap [Migrate to scoped storage] icon -> [Migrate]\r\n4. Wait for the migration to complete successfully\r\n\r\n### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nThe toast of \"Migration successful\" is shown in German (the language configured on AnkiDroid) as `Migration erfolgreich`\r\n\r\n### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nThe toast of \"Migration successful\" is shown in Spanish (the system language) as `Migraci\u00f3n exitosa`\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10436072/226325560-4821628a-ceeb-4eab-b318-3da8ee196db6.png\" width=\"320px\">\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10436072/226326117-562b481b-1ad2-4cee-b98d-90e36a159ae1.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Debug info\r\n\r\n```text\r\nAnkiDroid Version = 2.16alpha94\r\n\r\nAndroid Version = 11\r\n\r\nManufacturer = OPPO\r\n\r\nModel = CPH2013\r\n\r\nHardware = qcom\r\n\r\nWebview User Agent = Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 11; CPH2013 Build/RKQ1.200903.002; wv) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/4.0 Chrome/110.0.5481.153 Mobile Safari/537.36\r\n\r\nACRA UUID = 5030dae3-a0ba-453f-9da2-89735c9f64f0\r\n\r\nNew schema = false\r\n\r\nScheduler = std2\r\n\r\nCrash Reports Enabled = true\r\n\r\nDatabaseV2 Enabled = true\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n### (Optional) Anything else you want to share?\r\n\r\nN/A\r\n\r\n### Research\r\n\r\n- [X] I am reporting a bug specific to AnkiDroid (Android app)\r\n- [X] I have checked the [manual](https://ankidroid.org/docs/manual.html) and 